{"tid":1628572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢條友 捐款 堅定流？","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:00:09.000Z","uid":219334,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"980c7c07d4fc3e7d1c4cf8bce8429c58cf5745ae","tid":1628572,"uid":219334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"我呢幾日都見到呢位＂手足＂喺大圍八爪魚天橋派＂沙田加柚＂貼派，佢無主動要求人捐款，但佢就放咗個捐款箱喺度，D 人見度間中都會捐，我只想問大家佢係咪真手足，定係食緊血饅頭，我前日都捐咗比佢，唔想d 錢落入其他人手中，有冇人求証？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UiwTn1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUiwTn1N.jpg&h=2db637ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f651e58872bc2b3cef930c8699769a413dfded95","tid":1628572,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"用天貓箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a53ae63f670eb9f8195760dcb06fcf8400373e","tid":1628572,"uid":124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:49:25.000Z","msg":"之前Facebook group有人講過好似係大陸仔扮義士呃錢 <br />\n<br />\nps.唔肯定 搵唔返source<br />\n<br />\n唔好亂咁捐錢"},{"pid":"d0bcd83e8bf2de66b231519c0a168e38c2181393","tid":1628572,"uid":219334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5a53ae63f670eb9f8195760dcb06fcf8400373e","tid":1628572,"uid":124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:49:25.000Z","msg":"之前Facebook group有人講過好似係大陸仔扮義士呃錢 <br />\n<br />\nps.唔肯定 搵唔返source<br />\n<br />\n唔好亂咁捐錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:00:09.000Z","msg":"我見佢得一條友，附近冇條中坑好似幫佢睇緊水，唔肯定。但通常上八爪魚天橋都係一班年青人，一齊搞下連儂牆，呢條友呢幾日單拖同連續出見，所以我開始懷疑佢。如果佢係流嘅，必須要廣傳同趕走佢！"}]}